		title: "Tier 2 — Hybrid Refinery Bench"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:stone/1", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Build the Hybrid Refinery Bench. This machine requires Medium Voltage (MV) to High Voltage (HV) components and demands Nether and Undergarden boss drops as its combat gates.", "It can transmute gear rarity and reroll all affixes — powerful early-progression tools for pushing gear quality into Rare territory. Runs at 200 ticks per recipe. The Orb Forge runs the same recipes in 50."]
