		title: "The Chaos Orb"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/affix_reroll_all", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Forge a Chaos Orb (affix_reroll_all). Wipes and rerolls every affix on any item. Gate: Rare Stone + Undergarden Boss Drop + 2 Sulfur Dust.", "This is the equivalent of Path of Exile's Chaos Orb — use it to gamble on better affixes when a piece is nearly right."]
