		x: 12.0d
		y: 0.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000000500F"]
		title: "Tier 3 — Cipher Engraving Table"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:stone/3", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Build the Cipher Engraving Table. It requires Extreme Voltage (EV) to Insane Voltage (IV) components, and Blue Skies dimension boss trophies as its primary combat gates.", "This machine crafts the two Cipher orbs — which reroll the VALUES of existing prefixes or suffixes without changing which affixes are present — plus the Orb of Revelation for implicit stats. Runs at 300 ticks per recipe. The Orb Forge runs the same recipes in 75."]
