	}, {
		id: "0000000000005043"
		x: 17.0d
		y: 0.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000000501C", "0000000000040019"]
		title: "Tier 6 — Nano Reliquary"
		icon: {id: "dungeon_realm:uber_upgrade", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Build the Nano Reliquary — the sixth and final Orb Forge tier station. It requires a Mythic Salvage Stone AND a repeatable Endgame Boss Token as its dual combat gate.", "The Nano Reliquary gates on two things from outside this chapter: Tier 3 (the Cipher Engraving Table, built here) and the Fusion Forge from Chapter 13. Both must be complete before the Reliquary can be assembled. This is by design — the Reliquary's single output, the Stone of Hope, is the most powerful crafting option in the system and should not be accessible before the highest GT tier is in place.", "The only output is the Stone of Hope (dungeon_realm:uber_upgrade): a full item recreate that preserves the rarity floor. Use it when every affix on a piece is wrong and only the tier matters."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "0000000000005044"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "kubejs:endgame_boss_token", Count: 1b}
		}, {
