		x: 19.0d
		y: -0.5d
		dependencies: ["0000000000005043"]
		title: "Stone of Hope"
		icon: {id: "dungeon_realm:uber_upgrade", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Use the Nano Reliquary to forge a Stone of Hope. It recreates an item from scratch while preserving its rarity floor — the best outcome when every affix on a piece is wrong and only the tier matters. Gate: Mythic Stone + Endgame Boss Token + UIV Nano-component."]
		tasks: [{
