		id: "000000000000504A"
		x: 19.0d
		y: 0.5d
		dependencies: ["0000000000005043"]
		title: "The Unattainable Mirror"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/mirror", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Orb of Reflection (mmorpg:currency/mirror) is not craftable.", "It exists as a drop-only item to preserve the rare-item economy. A mirror-equivalent recipe would require a third non-stockpilable gate — something that cannot be farmed — and has not been designed yet.", "If you find one in the wild, treasure it."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000000504B"
			type: "checkmark"
			title: "Acknowledged: the Mirror is drop-only"
		}]
		rewards: []
	}, {
		id: "000000000000504C"
		x: 22.0d
		y: 0.0d
		dependencies: ["0000000000005043"]
		title: "The Orb Forge"
		icon: {id: "minecraft:nether_star", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Six machines. Two voltage tiers beyond EV. Assembly Lines, fusion reactors, the Warden's city, neutronium, osmiridium, the Nano Reliquary. All of it was preparation for this.", "The Orb Forge runs every recipe in the system — every orb from every station, Tier 1 through Tier 6. The Basic Modify Station processes an Orb of Quality in 100 ticks. The Orb Forge runs it in 25. The Fusion Forge builds a Sinistral Rebirth in 500 ticks. The Orb Forge runs it in 125. Same inputs. Same gates. A quarter of the wait.", "The six tier stations are not obsolete. They remain usable from whenever you build them. A player who reaches Tier 3 can run the Cipher Engraving Table through ZPM while working toward UHV. The Orb Forge is the reward for reaching the end of everything before it. Build it once and run everything through it."]
		tasks: [{
